{"tid":279134,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美國販毒新招：向中國網購","createTime":"2017-06-11T04:37:16.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-11T08:49:34.000Z","uid":13468,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e1aa8842c1aea47b89967981f0333a929280c113","tid":279134,"uid":13468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T04:37:16.000Z","msg":"美販毒新招：向中國網購<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n【本報綜合報道】美國緝毒局於去年十一月，在紐約市查獲一個由中國深圳寄出的包裹，內有一公斤的鴉片類藥物「呋喃基芬太尼」，揭發當地販毒集團逐漸改變固有獲取毒品的方法，轉而透過網絡從中國直接購入非法藥物，令當局更加難打擊販毒的活動。<br />\n警更難打擊販毒活動<br />\n<br />\n包裹疑是寄給紐約一名販毒集團成員，該成員與另外三十三人於今年三月，被控走私呋喃基芬太尼等毒品，他們否認控罪。當時該中國公司的名稱仍未浮面，直到近日才公開。美媒引述中國政府的登記資料指，該公司於去年八月組成，由一名叫Tang Li的女子持有，從事化妝品生產相關的藥物研究。<br />\n<br />\n美媒致電該公司時未能聯絡Tang Li，但由一名自稱是其友人及公司經理的張姓男子接聽。他否認公司寄出毒品包裹，又指他們沒出售芬太尼合成物。<br />\n<br />\n惟調查人員相信，愈來愈多販毒分子透過從中國直接網購毒品，避開警方的掃毒行動，同時省卻中間人的佣金。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/china_world/20170610/mobile/odn-20170610-0610_00180_030.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Forientaldaily.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Fchina_world%2F20170610%2Fmobile%2Fodn-20170610-0610_00180_030.html&d=J%2FdDR1h%2FRUzdpwiA6Y8oy9ibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=54b1443c\" target=\"_blank\">http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/china_world/20170610/mobile/odn-20170610-0610_00180_030.html</a>"},{"pid":"c3d39cfe5f7a51101ab5d810d9921a0a51e2aae9","tid":279134,"uid":49392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T04:40:29.000Z","msg":"點知毒品係假既"},{"pid":"7a1196a6a92b425cd3e4baa401d95435565bf938","tid":279134,"uid":56453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T04:42:23.000Z","msg":"淘寶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1d367bd144a5415fcabd9b3678cabe865b96705","tid":279134,"uid":56453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T04:42:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>淘寶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n連毒販都賣淘寶貨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a512a23f2fbecc4dd04331aa930f8e033afcf8b","tid":279134,"uid":13468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T04:44:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://www.localpresshk.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/1008_drug.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.localpresshk.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2016%2F10%2F1008_drug.jpg&h=26ca19b7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d2793c3a1d6d561fce5a6fcc9b6073295eb2059e","tid":279134,"uid":25367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T04:46:48.000Z","msg":"由香港帶奶粉去中國叫走水貨<br />\n咁由中國帶奶粉嚟香港叫咩？"},{"pid":"42d4750dfa6b9f29d3e4e2e7547717d18fe94f3c","tid":279134,"uid":4672,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T04:49:07.000Z","msg":"其實係支那政府默許賣毒品<br />\n<br />\n可以賺外匯"},{"pid":"2c2c3ae27b1779bb277762f0b1ed7fc814c6bdb9","tid":279134,"uid":13468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T04:49:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2016/10/09/672055-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2016%2F10%2F09%2F672055-XXL.jpg&h=65f21179&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"48048a194dea84b23ee895ff2ff710c32be0d760","tid":279134,"uid":58503,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T04:52:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點知毒品係假既</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好大機會"},{"pid":"bb18bd8eb3c569421630a4ecf1086c8fd26583a5","tid":279134,"uid":13468,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T04:52:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實係支那政府默許賣毒品<br />\n<br />\n可以賺外匯</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2016/10/09/672053-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2016%2F10%2F09%2F672053-XXL.jpg&h=8acfb499&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"378b9f4d2ce7b3ce90836cb47146ae0ee3d43eb9","tid":279134,"uid":18772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T07:53:48.000Z","msg":"大陸大把合成藥粉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n呢隻唔通過咪生產另一隻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f442496f030e04a5c1a1e74ca8aff1e0ef30b5e","tid":279134,"uid":13468,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T08:08:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>大陸大把合成藥粉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n呢隻唔通過咪生產另一隻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://sc01.alicdn.com/kf/HTB1JKtDLFXXXXaTXFXXq6xXFXXX9/Stock-Lab-Fine-Chemical-Nootropic-NSI-189.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsc01.alicdn.com%2Fkf%2FHTB1JKtDLFXXXXaTXFXXq6xXFXXX9%2FStock-Lab-Fine-Chemical-Nootropic-NSI-189.jpg&h=75c0bad7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nNSI-189是一個實驗性藥物,由Neuralstem, Inc.開發的抗抑鬱藥。用於治療重性抑鬱障礙 (MDD), 認知障礙以及神經退行性疾病.<br />\n<br />\n相關研究由美國國防高等研究計劃署 (DARPA)以及國立衛生研究院 (NIH)出資。<br />\n NSI-189的作用機轉為在海馬迴增強的神經元新生以及其體積的增大，但NSI-189達成此效果的機轉尚不明朗。配體結合研究目前為止無法找出其標靶<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/NSI-189\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2FNSI-189&d=J%2FdDR1h%2FRUzdpwiA6Y8oy9ibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=212df8e7\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/NSI-189</a><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86fd7f39dd3c76b2d75a61c9d6a3ce226a5c5282","tid":279134,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T08:16:45.000Z","msg":"如果d貨俾人截咗 邊個負責？"},{"pid":"240e579f49e9c5a78995ba9cda66e103db458409","tid":279134,"uid":13468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T08:49:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>如果d貨俾人截咗 邊個負責？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n買家負責"}]}